sourcesContent: import React from "react"; export const Transaction = ({ created, ref, collectionMethod, amtRecvd, xchangeRate, totalCharge, totalPaid, rcverName, rcverPhone, rcverId, senderName, senderPhone, status }) => ( {created} {ref} {collectionMethod} {amtRecvd} {xchangeRate} {totalCharge} {totalPaid} {rcverName} {rcverPhone} {rcverId} {senderName} {senderPhone} {status} );
